A "smart" planner that determines when to study, work on assignments, etc. You must have a Google account because it works with Tasks and Calendar.

## Did it run:
Yes(Eventually)

## Issues encountered:
Required several additional downloads and ran on older Python.

## Usefulness:
Good example to compare to, but running on old Python and the other issues leads to me wanting to look for other examples.
